 However, the aforementioned advantages of SQLite give plenty of reasons
 to choose SQLite over 
\family typewriter
shelve
\family default
.
 Plus, SQLite is thoroughly tested, even against corruption 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "SQLite testing"

\end_inset

