 of them are not used at all.
 
\family typewriter
pngcrush
\family default
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "pngcrush"

\end_inset

 is used to strip all the unneeded chunks.
 
\family typewriter
pngcrush
\family default
